reut2-015.sgm, IRT PROPERTY LAUNCHES DEBENTURE IN EUROMARKET, IRT Property Co, a real estate investmenttrust based in Atlanta, Georgia, has launched a 30 mln dlrconvertible subordinated debenture in the Euromarket, a partnerof Chandler Partnership Ltd said.    The issue is unique in several respects and is only one ofa handful of such deals to be brought to this market, he said.    Unlike most eurobonds, the issue will not be underwritten.Instead, IRT mandated Chandler Partnership to find potentialinvestors with whom the issue can be preplaced and to thenplace on a best efforts" basis what ever amount may not besubscribed.    Chandler itself was set up in the Isle of Jersey in themiddle of last year as a partnership

